OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773223748
OL,3,CThousands protest at US embassy
OL,4,Ccalling for end to strikes on Iran
OL,6,FThousands of protesters calling for
OL,7,Fthe end of US and Israeli strikes on
OL,8,FIran have marched to the US embassy in
OL,9,Fcentral London.
OL,11,FGroups including the Campaign for
OL,12,FNuclear Disarmament (CND), Stop The
OL,13,FWar, Palestine Solidarity Campaign,
OL,14,FMuslim Association Of Britain,
OL,15,FPalestinian Forum in Britain and
OL,16,FFriends Of Al-Aqsa led the march to
OL,17,Fthe embassy on Saturday afternoon,
OL,18,Fafter gathering on Millbank, near
OL,19,FWestminster.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
