OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773223748
OL,3,CThousands protest at US embassy
OL,4,Ccalling for end to strikes on Iran
OL,6,FMany protesters were carrying Iranian
OL,7,Fand Palestinian flags as well as
OL,8,Fportraits of Iran's former supreme
OL,9,Fleader Ayatollah Khamenei, who was
OL,10,Fkilled in the opening strike of the
OL,11,Fwar last Saturday.
OL,13,FSome waved placards reading "Stop
OL,14,FTrump's Wars", "Stop the War on Iran",
OL,15,F"Stop Arming Israel" and "No War on
OL,16,FIran".
OL,18,FOutside the US embassy in Vauxhall,
OL,19,FYour Party MP Zarah Sultana told
OL,20,Fprotesters: "we will not be ignored
OL,21,Fagain."
OL,26,@uD@]OUvD@MO]vD@POUvD@eO]wD@AOUwD@TO]wD@
OL,26,AZOUxD@EO]|D@MOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773223748
OL,3,CThousands protest at US embassy
OL,4,Ccalling for end to strikes on Iran
OL,6,FRecalling the 2003 US-led invasion of
OL,7,FIraq that toppled dictator Saddam
OL,8,FHussein, she told the crowd: "Back
OL,9,Fthen, we were told that Iraq had
OL,10,Fweapons of mass destruction.
OL,12,F"We were told that war would bring
OL,13,Fpeace and democracy.
OL,15,F"We were told that the war would
OL,16,Fprotect Iraqis and protect the world,
OL,17,Fbut the truth was very different."
OL,19,FThe former Labour MP, who represents
OL,20,FCoventry South, added: "The children
OL,21,Fof Baghdad deserve to grow up.
OL,26,@pD@^OUtD@AOUwD@AOUyD@bO]|D@XOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773223748
OL,3,CThousands protest at US embassy
OL,4,Ccalling for end to strikes on Iran
OL,6,F"And 23 years ago, when we marched
OL,7,Fagainst the Iraq war, we were ignored.
OL,9,F"We will not be ignored again, because
OL,10,Fhistory proved them right, and today,
OL,11,Fwe raise our voices for peace, for
OL,12,Fjustice and for a world where
OL,13,Fgovernments learn the lessons of the
OL,14,Fpast."
OL,16,FA statement from Islington North MP
OL,17,Fand former Labour leader Jeremy
OL,18,FCorbyn, who could not attend the
OL,19,Fprotest, was read to the crowd outside
OL,20,Fthe embassy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773223748
OL,3,CThousands protest at US embassy
OL,4,Ccalling for end to strikes on Iran
OL,6,FIt read: "In 2003, hundreds of
OL,7,Fthousands of us protested against the
OL,8,Fillegal invasion of Iraq, and we were
OL,9,Fignored, but we are here today to say
OL,10,Floudly and clearly: do not drag
OL,11,FBritain into another illegal war."
OL,13,FIn the statement, Mr Corbyn, now an
OL,14,FIndependent MP, said: "For too long,
OL,15,Fthe UK has blindly followed the US as
OL,16,Fit indulges in catastrophic
OL,17,Finterventions around the world.
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@bO]vD@WOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/11
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773223748
OL,3,CThousands protest at US embassy
OL,4,Ccalling for end to strikes on Iran
OL,6,F"We are here to defend something
OL,7,Fdifferent, a foreign policy based on
OL,8,Fco-operation, equality and
OL,9,Fsovereignty."
OL,11,FHe added: "Forever war is not a game.
OL,12,FIt has real-life human consequences,
OL,13,Fand US and Israel must be held
OL,14,Faccountable for their prize."
OL,16,FBetween 5,000 and 6,000 protesters
OL,17,Fmarched from Millbank to the US
OL,18,Fembassy on Saturday afternoon,
OL,19,Faccording to a police officer who was
OL,20,Fwalking alongside the crowd.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@MO]sD@KOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/11
