CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773223748
OL,3,CThousands protest at US embassy
OL,4,Ccalling for end to strikes on Iran
OL,6,FIn an update on X, the Metropolitan
OL,7,FPolice said it arrested one woman
OL,8,Fduring the protest.
OL,10,FThe force said: "A woman in her 60s
OL,11,Fhas been arrested on suspicion of
OL,12,Finciting racial hatred in relation to
OL,13,Fa placard."
OL,15,FBefore the event, the Met Police
OL,16,Fstepped up patrols and imposed
OL,17,Fconditions requiring protesters to
OL,18,Fstay on a designated route and finish
OL,19,Ftheir post-march rally by 5pm.
OL,26,@rD@QOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/11
