PN,40908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773223748
OL,3,CThousands protest at US embassy
OL,4,Ccalling for end to strikes on Iran
OL,6,FSeveral groups of people holding
OL,7,FIsraeli flags were standing on the
OL,8,Fside of Millbank as protesters calling
OL,9,Ffor the end of US and Israeli strikes
OL,10,Fon Iran were on their way to the
OL,11,Fembassy.
OL,13,FMany protesters could be heard
OL,14,Fshouting "shame on you" and
OL,15,F"murderers" to the people holding
OL,16,FIsraeli flags, to which some replied
OL,17,F"you're wrong", "you're in denial".
OL,26,@vD@JOUvD@WO]wD@AOUwD@KO]yD@AOUyD@NO]yD@
OL,26,AQOUyD@bO]
