PN,40909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773223748
OL,3,CThousands protest at US embassy
OL,4,Ccalling for end to strikes on Iran
OL,6,FDemonstrators leading the march could
OL,7,Fbe heard chanting: "We are the people.
OL,8,FWe won't be silenced. Stop the bombing
OL,9,Fnow, now, now, now."
OL,11,FDaniela Costa, a 30-year-old Brazilian
OL,12,Fstudent living in London, said: "I'm
OL,13,Ffrom Brazil. I just came here to show
OL,14,Fsolidarity, both to Iran and
OL,15,FPalestine, but also to Cuba and
OL,16,FVenezuela."
OL,18,FShe added: "I just feel that we can't
OL,19,Fjust live as if it's just business as
OL,20,Fusual at this moment.
OL,26,@oD@TOUqD@TO]tD@aOUxD@KO]zD@LOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/11
