PN,40910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773223748
OL,3,CThousands protest at US embassy
OL,4,Ccalling for end to strikes on Iran
OL,6,F"I expect that this protest will show
OL,7,Fthe UK Government that they don't have
OL,8,Fpopular support to participate in the
OL,9,Fwar in any way, such as providing
OL,10,Fweapons or providing their... military
OL,11,Fbases to the US."
OL,13,FAsked about why he attended the
OL,14,Fprotest, Martin Perry, 58, from
OL,15,FNorthampton, said: "Because the acts
OL,16,Fagainst Iran is against international
OL,17,Flaw, and it's just a pattern of
OL,18,Fevents, decisions taken by America and
OL,19,FIsrael, that are destroying
OL,20,Finternational law."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@QO]wD@TOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/11
