FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773223748
OL,3,CThousands protest at US embassy
OL,4,Ccalling for end to strikes on Iran
OL,6,FHe added: "I'm here today to signal to
OL,7,FKeir Starmer that the public aren't
OL,8,Ffor the war against Iran, and don't
OL,9,Fwant our forces going into, being
OL,10,Finvolved in an illegal war."
OL,12,FThe organisers of Saturday's
OL,13,Fdemonstration said a march "against
OL,14,Fthe far right" will take place on
OL,15,FMarch 28 in central London.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@\O]uD@\OUvD@NO]
